il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.parser.experiment.analysis

Class SempreExperimentAnalysis

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.parser.experiment.analysis.SempreExperimentAnalysis

  • public class SempreExperimentAnalysis
extends java.lang.Object
    All the analysis and results data associated with an SempreExperiment. Meant to be saved persistently as file tree (hence not serializable).
